{
  "page": "Fight at the Fist",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Fight at the Fist</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Zippo514_BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Zippo514 BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Zippo514_BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg/350px-Zippo514_BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"190\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Zippo514_BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg/525px-Zippo514_BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/Zippo514_BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg/700px-Zippo514_BattleoftheFistFirstMenII.jpg 2x\" /></a><div><div style=\"width:100%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;\">The Battle of the Fist of the First Men - by zippo514 ©</div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Conflict_beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Conflict beyond the Wall\">Conflict beyond the Wall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">Fist of the First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">300 men</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Hundreds of <a href=\"/index.php/Wights\" title=\"Wights\">wights</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">~ 250 with more dying on the retreat<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Thoren_Smallwood\" title=\"Thoren Smallwood\">Thoren Smallwood</a>†<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Ottyn_Wythers\" title=\"Ottyn Wythers\">Ottyn Wythers</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>fight at the Fist</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is a lopsided loss for the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. Taking place on the <a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">Fist of the First Men</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a>, the Night's Watch is unable to defend against the <a href=\"/index.php/Wights\" title=\"Wights\">wights</a> sent against them.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Background\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Background</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Battle\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Battle</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Background\">Background</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fight_at_the_Fist&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Background\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord Commander <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a> leads three hundred men <a href=\"/index.php/Great_ranging\" title=\"Great ranging\">on an expedition</a> beyond the Wall, with two hundred men from <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a> and the rest from the <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Tower\" title=\"Shadow Tower\">Shadow Tower</a>, in search of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a> and, if possible, to discover the whereabouts of <a href=\"/index.php/Benjen_Stark\" title=\"Benjen Stark\">Benjen Stark</a>. Finding neither, Lord Commander Mormont choses the <a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">Fist of the First Men</a>, an ancient ringfort, as his base of operations while he sends out scouting parties in search of information. \n</p><p>From the Fist, Mormont hopes to stop any march on the Wall. He strengthens their defenses with spikes and pits, caltrops scattered on the slopes, and a ring of watchers around the camp and along the river to warn of any approach.\n</p><p>When the men arrive at the Fist they make camp. <a href=\"/index.php/Dywen\" title=\"Dywen\">Dywen</a> feels that it smells cold, while <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> thinks it smells like death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle\">Battle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fight_at_the_Fist&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Battle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While waiting for the last of the search parties to return to decide on a plan of action regarding the <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a>, the Watch are attacked by hundreds of <a href=\"/index.php/Wights\" title=\"Wights\">wights</a>, both human and <a href=\"/index.php/Animal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Animal\">animal</a>. Their volleys of arrows have no effect against the undead attackers and Mormont orders them to use fire arrows, slowing the wights but not stopping them. The Watch is quickly overrun, but Mormont is able to form up about fifty survivors to break out of the Fist.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fight_at_the_Fist&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After a crushing defeat, the majority of the Night's Watch who fight on the Fist are slain by the insurmountable odds. Those who survive are led by Jeor Mormont on a grim march back to <a href=\"/index.php/Craster%27s_Keep\" title=\"Craster&#39;s Keep\">Craster's Keep</a> where the next <a href=\"/index.php/Mutiny_at_Craster%27s_Keep\" title=\"Mutiny at Craster&#39;s Keep\">disaster</a> occurs.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fight_at_the_Fist&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Jon</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">The Old Bear</a> commanded. <a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">This place</a> was high and strong, and he made it stronger. He dug pits and planted stakes, laid up food and water. He was ready for ...<br />\n<b>Mance</b>: ... me? Aye, he was. Had I been fool enough to storm this hill, I might have lost five men for every <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">crow</a> I slew and still counted myself lucky. But when <a href=\"/index.php/Wights\" title=\"Wights\">the dead</a> walk, walls and stakes and swords mean nothing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Sam … would you wake me, please? I am having this terrible nightmare.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Dolorous_Edd\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dolorous Edd\">Dolorous Edd</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fight_at_the_Fist&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, Samwell I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Jon IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Samwell II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Jon II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width: